## Troubleshooting

**"npm not found"** → Node.js wasn't installed correctly. Reinstall from nodejs.org

**"eas not found"** → Run `npm install -g eas-cli` again

**Build fails with "credentials error"** → Run `eas credentials` and follow prompts

**App crashes on start** → Run `npx expo start` and check the error in terminal

